    "causal_summary": "Add a ReAct-style agentic strategy to the Memory MCP's `memory_context` mode router so that complex asks get an LLM-driven reason-act-observe retrieval loop over the existing memory tools, instead of a single straight-line search call. Research (028/007, iterations 11/17/22) confirmed the strategy seam is clean and additive, but blast-radius scoping corrected the original H/L \"best lev/eff\" rating down to **L effort**: the loop injects an LLM into a synchronous, deterministic, pure better-sqlite3 retrieval hot path, and **no loop/cost governor exists anywhere today** — controller, step-cap, cost-ceiling, and stop-condition are all greenfield. This is its own design packet, prove-first, gated default-off.",
